name: Sampler Photobook
description: A 40 page book of Misty Skye Photography scenic photos. All photos are taken in New England. This is a GREAT coffee table book to show off to your family and friends! The book measures 12x12 with full color and black and white prints. Photos are printed on premium paper for optimum viewing. All prints are "Photographers Choice" and are the best of the best! Also comes with a subscription to the Misty Skye Photography Newsletter which includes a photo of the month, monthly coupons and tips and tricks from the photographers desk!

name: Stand out Image.
